      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">MM is valid in SOWPODS (International) but NOT in TWL (North American). At 6 points from just 2 tiles, MM is one of the highest-scoring two-letter words in the game — because each M is worth 3 points. It's an interjection expressing pleasure or agreement ("mmm, that's delicious"), and crucially, it contains no vowels. A perfect emergency play when consonants dominate your rack.</p>

